item.title: Proxy Problems
item.author: adas59@asu.edu (Amitabh Das)
item.description: Just completed the campus to corporate training at Oracle MySQL and ready to start! At the end of our training, we were given a task to complete to “refresh our C++ skills”. We were to design a program which would simulate MySQL on a smaller scale – Multiple clients, shared data structures, locks and a few more features. Of course I started off almost immediately but I came across a problem.
